> Martin Jr., D. Michael wrote:
>    What are all you other bus folks doing out there when you camp and/or
> go to shows?

I've become a minimalist in my later years and I throw a blue tarp
over the bus, bungied to the wheelwell on the drivers side and two PVC
poles I made on the front side, if I can't find a nearby tree.  keep
doors closed to keep out bugs, and have couple pieces of sreening I
magneticly put over the windows that I have opened....

